  <name>MultiScope</name>
  <summary>Multi-instance Gamescope manager</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      MultiScope is a powerful tool for managing multiple Gamescope instances
      with advanced configuration options. It provides an intuitive GUI for
      creating and managing gaming profiles with custom display settings,
      input devices, and window management.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Create and manage multiple Gamescope profiles</li>
      <li>Advanced display configuration (resolution, refresh rate, scaling)</li>
      <li>Virtual input device management</li>
      <li>KDE window manager integration</li>
      <li>GTK4/Adwaita modern interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

